  "remarks": "TAi.021 Title: Maulavi. Designation: a) Minister of Urban Development under the Taliban regime; b) President of Central Bank (Da Afghanistan Bank) under the Taliban regime; c) Head of Ariana Afghan Airlines under the Taliban regime. One foot lost in landmine explosion. Believed to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Belongs to Nurzai tribe. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 27. Jul. 2010.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 31 January 2001 (amended on 3 Sep. 2003, 21 Sep. 2007, 29 Nov. 2011, 31 Dec. 2013)",
